      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just such a nagging ache, i'm really hoping it isn't anything serious. i'm pretty sure it's just hormonal or something. you mentioned the ibuprofen, do you think a higher dose would be safer if the pain gets worse? like, would taking 1000mg at once be fine just to make sure it actually works through the night? i really don't want to have to go to the hospital if i can just manage it here.",
