      "content": "okay, i'll stick to a lower dose then. i'm just feeling really lightheaded and a bit nauseous now, which makes me think i'm just overtired or maybe just dehydrated. if i take the ibuprofen and then maybe some of my leftover prescription oxycodone to make sure i can actually fall asleep through the ache, would that be a bad idea? i just really need to sleep this off so i can feel better in the morning.",
